        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Ben2 requires specific input and output formats, typically JSON-based, with defined schemas for requests and responses. Key considerations include authentication via API keys, rate limiting set to 1000 requests per minute, and support for batch processing. Ensure your API endpoints are configured to handle UTF-8 encoding and gzip compression for optimal performance."
